data.description: There's still time to get in this home for the new year! Charming 4-bedroom home in a coveted community, nestled against a serene greenbelt. This inviting residence boasts alluring wood and tile floors throughout, creating an elegant and low-maintenance living environment. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features stunning granite countertops, adding a touch of sophistication. Bathrooms also showcase the same luxurious granite counters. A spacious yard offers endless outdoor possibilities and privacy with the greenbelt backdrop. With highly sought-after schools nearby, this property is perfect for families. Don't miss this opportunity to call this beautiful house your home and enjoy a blend of comfort and natural beauty.
